metadata.name: Black Nights Stars
metadata.description:
This is the 1 NFT in a collection of 7 photographs that have been issued as a single, unique edition.

Photo: 7500Ñ…10000 px

White and black - the beginning and the end.
 
Black is the absolute limit beyond which life ceases. It conveys the idea of nothingness and disappearance. 

White is a clean slate on which history will be written.
